    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That sounds a bit like you're just picking a side there. Most economists say that tariffs actually slow down growth and hurt everyone in the long run by distorting the market. Why are you framing the protectionist view as the \"strategic\" way to go instead of just presenting both sides as valid debates?",
